 ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Processing instruction indicating the page is a template.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::protect_instruction" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Protect Instruction</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Processing instruction indicating the page is protected from modification and deletion.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::deprecate_instruction" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Deprecate Instruction</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Processing instruction indicating the page needs to be deleted.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::appversion" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">AppVersion</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Displays the wiki engine version.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::lastmodified" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">LastModified</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Displays the modified date/time of the page.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::created" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Created</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Displays the created date/time of the page.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::name" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Name</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Displays the pages name.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::navigation" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Navigation</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Diaplys the URL friendly navigation name of a page.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::title_standard_function" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Title (Standard Function)</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Displays the title of the wiki page in title format.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::toc" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">TOC</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Generate a table-of-contents for a page from the headings.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::attachments" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Attachments</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Lists the attached files associated with a page.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::revisions" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Revisions</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Displays the revision history of a page.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::hr" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">HR</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Inserts a horizontal rule (divider) into the wiki bosy.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::br" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">BR</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Inserts one or more line-breaks into the wiki body.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::inject" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Inject</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Inserts the un-processed wiki body of one page into the calling page.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::editlink" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">EditLink</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Insert a link to quickly edit the page.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::tags_standard_function" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Tags (Standard Function)</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Display the tags associated with the page.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::file" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">File</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Insert file download links into the wiki body.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::image" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Image</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Display images in the wiki body.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::tagcloud" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">TagCloud</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Create a tag cloud from a seed tag.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::textglossary" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">TextGlossary</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Create a glossary from a search of wiki body contens.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::recentlymodified" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">RecentlyModified</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Display a list of recently modified wiki pages.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::tagglossary" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">TagGlossary</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Create a glossary from a search of specified tags.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::searchcloud" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">SearchCloud</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Create a cloud of pages from a search of wiki body contents.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::taglist" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">TagList</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Create a list of pages from a search of page tags.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::searchlist" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">SearchList</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Create  a list from a search of wiki body contents.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::tags_instruction_function" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Tags (Instruction Function)</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Associate tags with a page.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::color" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Color</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Set the color of a portion of text.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::get" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Get</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Get wiki page variable value.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::set" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Set</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Set wiki page variable value.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::collapse" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Collapse</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Dynamically show or hide a section of the wiki body.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::card" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Card</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Cards are good for displaying every-day content and can have a title.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::foreground" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Foreground</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Set the foreground color for a block of content.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::background" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Background</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Set the background color for a block of content.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::callout" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Callout</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Prominently display useful information in a fairly understated panel.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::jumbotron" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Jumbotron</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Large grey box good for calling attention in a non-critical way.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::bullets" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Bullets</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Create hierarchical ordered or unordered lists.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::code" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Code</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">Display formatted, wiki-unprocessed and syntax-hilighted code.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::wiki_help" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Wiki Help</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">All the wiki help, all in one place.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::whitespace" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Whitespace</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div class="small text-body-secondary text-truncate">How the wiki handles whitespace and what you can do to manipulate it.</div></div><div class="border-bottom"><a href="/wiki_help::links" class="d-block text-reset py-2"><span class="fw-semibold text-truncate">Links</span><span class="small text-body-secondary text-nowrap ms-2">(8/28/2023 7:53 PM)</span></a><div clas